  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT19">
<l>muṟṟārā vaṉamulaiyāḷ pāvai māyaṉ</l>
<l>moyyakalat tuḷḷiruppā ḷaḵtuṅ kaṇṭum</l>
<l>aṟṟāḷtaṉ niṟaivaḻintā ḷāvik kiṉṟā</l>
<l>ḷaṇiyaraṅka māṭutumō tōḻī yeṉṉum</l>
<l>peṟṟēṉvāyc colliṟaiyum pēcak kēḷāḷ</l>
<l>pērppāṭit taṇkuṭantai nakarum pāṭi</l>
<l>poṟṟāma raikkayamnī rāṭap pōṉāḷ</l>
<l>poruvaṟṟā ḷeṉmakaḷum poṉṉu maḵtē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As soon as seeing that the girl with unmatured, beautiful breasts</l>
<l rend="indent">will be the one on Māyaṉ’s strong chest,</l>
<l>She was thus. She, whose perfection was ruined, sighs;</l>
<l rend="indent">she says, “Friend, shall we dance in ornate Araṅkam?”</l>
<l>As I who begot [her] speak, she does not hear a single word [from my] mouth!</l>
<l rend="indent">Singing of Pēr [and] singing of the cool city of Kuṭantai,</l>
<l>She has gone to bathe in Golden Lotus tank.</l>
<l rend="indent">[Ladies,] my girl is without comparison; are your golden [girls] also [like] that?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
